  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] You may suspend 1 of your Digimon. Then,
    gain 1 memory for each suspended Digimon with [Vegetation] or [Fairy] in their
    traits you have in play. If you gain 2 or more memory by this effect, unsuspend
    this Digimon and it gains \uFF1CPiercing\uFF1E for the turn.[Your Turn] For every
    2 suspended Digimon you have in play, this Digimon gets +2000 DP and gains \uFF1CSecurity
    Attack +1\uFF1E."
